### Registrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Felipe Teste",
  "email": "felipe@teste.com",
  "password": "senha12345"
}

### Fazer login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "felipe@teste.com",
  "password": "senha12345"
}
